entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Gen yon grenn pwoblèm, yo vle ekzakteman menm bagay avè nou." t="Only problem is, dey want exactly de same thing we want." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Fanm lan? Li konnen sa nap chache a?" t="De woman? And dey know what we looking for?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Wi, yo konnen." t="Yes, they know." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou kwè NetWatch gen moun nan mitan nou?" t="You think NetWatch has people here, among us?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Se Plasid ki ta sipoze nan GIM nan." t="Placide is de one who should be in de GIM." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen panse netrènèz pa yo bon men jan ak pa nou, si yo pa pi bon menm." t="I think dey netrunners are just as good as ours, if not better." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Men mwen pap janm di sa pou Brigitte." t="But I would never say dat to Brigitte." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Brigitte kapab degaje li pou kont li." t="Brigitte will manage on her own." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Wi, gade kijan bagay yo pase, hm?" t="Yeah, and look how dat turn out, hm?" b="" a=""/>
